2000-08-07  Rebecca Schulman  <rebecka@eazel.com>

	* libmedusa-internal/medusa-text-index-plaintext-module.c:
	only index words, not numbers.
	* indexer/medusa-file-index-daemon.c: (copy_new_index_files):
